      "content": {
        "en": {
          "title": "The goal that tilted it",
          "html": "<p>Saibari’s goal decided a tight contest and gave Morocco a 1-0 win. He made 28 runs in behind Scotland’s defence, with 13 of those turned into passes received — a reliable outlet for his side. The midfielder’s movement kept pressure on Scotland’s back line and helped Morocco secure the points.</p>"
        },
        "zh": {
          "title": "萨伊巴里一锤定音，摩洛哥 1-0 胜苏格兰",
          "html": "<p>萨伊巴里打入全场唯一进球，助摩洛哥 1-0 战胜苏格兰。</p><p>中场推进时，他 28 次尝试身后接应，成功 13 次，梳理了向前出球路线。</p><p>全场跑动超过 10 公里，兼顾了中场接应与进攻终结。</p>"
        }
